This is quite excellent for a first skip. I always love it when people are able to bring examples of genre fiction that usually don’t do well in this format into an article. Ie 1875’s jump scare, 3999’s stream of consciousness, or 1730’s novella length storyline. This one succeeds in bringing office romance and even romcom style plotting into an SCP, and in such a way that I didn’t feel skeptical at its inclusion or presentation. Well done, and I look forward to seeing your future works.







